  "body": "## Description\r\n\r\nImplement a *fast* way to sync the beacon node from scratch using a checkpoint state. See [this video by Adrian Sutton](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ce9uVRl23zI) from the Teku development team. You can get more details on [the related Teku documentation page](https://docs.teku.pegasys.tech/en/latest/HowTo/Get-Started/Checkpoint-Start/).\r\n\r\n## Present Behaviour\r\n\r\nIt can take a few hours to sync a Lighthouse beacon node on mainnet or any of the testnet from scratch.\r\n\r\n## Expected Behaviour\r\n\r\nIt should take only 2 minutes to sync a Lighthouse beacon node from scratch using a recent finalized checkpoint state.\r\n\r\n## Steps to resolve\r\n\r\nImplement syncing using a provided checkpoint state.\r\n",
